text: Food is great, paired with my favorite red wines. My friends and I had enjoyed ourselves. All the staff services (trainees) are excellent and attentive. Big shoutout to Mr Stanley, the dedicated team head for the outlet! Will visit again next time :)
Went with family tonight. The food is pretty good, especially the Harry truffles pizza. Thank you for the service. Will come again. The only challenge is the location of the restaurant.

Bar bites such as the satay, tomyum popcorn chicken were addictively delish, definitely recommended. Mains we tried included the seafood aglio olio, burger, chicken and fish & chips. Fish & chips were the most satisfying in terms of taste and portion for its price. The rest of the dishes were alright. Attentive staff and nice, quieter atmosphere away from the crowds.
Best wings in Tampines, cool off the Menu items if you dare to ask. Stanley, Sarah, Lex and Rohit makes the place feels like an extension of your living room.
Thank you Stanley and team for the wonderful service. Very attentive and food is great. Worth coming!
